<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Cancelled - Kids World</title>
    <style>
        /* Shared Styles */
        body, html { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
        .container { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4); border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; padding: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea; }
        .content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; margin: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #ff5a5f; }
        .order-id { font-weight: bold; color: #333; background: #eee; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 4px; }
        .refund-box { background-color: #f9f9f9; border-left: 4px solid #ff5a5f; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #666; padding: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Kids World</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
                <p>Your order <span class="order-id">#<%= orderId %></span> has been cancelled.</p>
                
                <div class="refund-box">
                    <strong>Refund Status:</strong>
                    <p>Amount Refunded to Wallet: ₹<%= refundedAmount %></p>
                    <p>Cancellation Fee: ₹<%= cancellationFee %></p>
                </div>

                <p>If you have any questions regarding this cancellation, please contact our support team.</p>
                <p>We hope to see you again soon!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Best regards,<br>The Kids World Team</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>